"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/can-men-ever-wear-shorts-to-the-office-what-about-baseball-caps-our-poll-results-may-surprise-you-9449440f?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">男士可以穿短裤去办公室吗？棒球帽怎么样？我们的民意调查结果可能会让您感到惊讶。</a></h3><h4>我们对 1,000 多名美国成年人进行了调查，了解男士现在可以穿哪些休闲单品去上班。通常，世代之间存在分歧。 <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/can-men-ever-wear-shorts-to-the-office-what-about-baseball-caps-our-poll-results-may-surprise-you-9449440f?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">读故事。</a> </h4><div class="media-object scope-
